milestones.description: Jonty Rhodes has broken the record for most catches (20) in ODIs for SA, going past McMillan's 19
Richardson and Fanie de Villiers's 30-run partnership is SA's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 21 between Omar Henry and McMillan
